  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_1' aria-label=\" S.C. Garg versus State of Uttar Pradesh & Anr. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('1','2025','2025_5_627_652','2025INSC493'); ><font size='4'> <strong>S.C. GARG<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>STATE OF UTTAR PRADESH & ANR. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 5 S.C.R. 627</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 493</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010001772025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : PANKAJ MITHAL, PRASHANT KUMAR MISHRA</strong><br> Issue for Consideration The appellant&rsquo;s petition u/s.482 of the Criminal Procedure Code, 1973 seeking quashment of Criminal Case No. 7489 of 2002 pending on the file of Chief Judicial Magistrate for offences u/s.420 of the Penal Code, 1860 was dismissed by the High Court. Headnotes&dagger; s.482 &ndash; Negotiable Instrument Act, 1881 &ndash; s.138 &ndash; Penal Code, 1860 &ndash; s.420 &ndash; The appellant&rsquo;s company filed a complaint u/s.138 of the NI Act against ID Packaging and respondent no.2 in relation to the 07 dishonored cheques &ndash; The trial Court convicted<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 15-04-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CRIMINAL APPEAL No. 438/2018</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('1','2025','2025_5_627_652','2025INSC493','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('1','2025','2025_5_627_